Version 2.0
-----------
* Refactoring:
  - Unused classes removed.
  - Uses SLF4J.
* Compatible with Java SE 6 and Java SE 7.
* Project build with maven.

Version 1.6.2
-------------
* ExtendedProtocolSocketFactory.getSSLContext() method is now public.

Version 1.6.1
-------------
* bug fix: handling of secure cookies (HTTPS).

Version 1.6.0
-------------
* downloadConfiguration(URL url) method added to create a XML config from an external URL.
* Version set in jar MANIFEST.
* glite-slcs-common package jar named *WITHOUT* version number: glite-slcs-common.jar
 

Version 1.5.1
-------------
* glite-slcs-common package jar named with version number. example: glite-slcs-common-1.5.1.jar
* RFC2253 compliant escaping method Utils.escapeAttributeValue(string) added.

Version 1.5.0
-------------
* X509PrincipalUtil utility class to handle certificate subject DN with literal and RDN. BouncyCastle X509Name and X509Principal bug workaround implemented.
* PKCS10 uses the X509PrincipalUtil utility class to validate and normalize the DN.

Version 1.4.0
-------------
* Packaging with ETICS new jakarta-commons-* JPackage packages. Don't use old commons-* packages anymore.
* Dependencies on JPackage jakarta-commons-* packages.

Version 1.3.0
-------------
* Utils.setFilePermissions doesn't show error for Windows.
* FileConfigurationMonitor uses File obj as argument and not FileConfiguration anymore.

Version 1.2.0
-------------
* XML configuration file should not escape , (comma) anymore.
* Threading replaced by Timer and TimerTask, more secure.

Version 1.1.0
-------------
* PKCS12 handling added in Codec

Version 1.0.0
-------------
* initial version
--
$Id: CHANGELOG,v 1.13 2010/02/09 09:08:04 vtschopp Exp $
